name: PhiHenna Black
description: Beside the effect similar to permanent makeup Phi Henna, with all its natural benefits, provides multiple advantages for the brow hairs by helping to refine and revive weak eyebrow hair follicles, encouraging their vitality and keeping their natural shape.
